last_episode_to_air.name: End of Summer Daze
last_episode_to_air.overview: Summer is over, and SpongeBob and Patrick stay behind for one final attempt to catch a jellyfish – but they’re not the only ones hiding out at camp.

name: Kamp Koral: SpongeBob's Under Years
overview: SpongeBob and friends spend the summer catching jellyfish, building camp-fires, and swimming in Lake Yuckymuck at Camp Coral, located in the Kelp Forest.

episodes.name: The Jellyfish Kid
episodes.overview: A young SpongeBob is determined to catch his first jellyfish, so his friends do whatever they can to help him.

episodes.name: Sugar-Squeeze!
episodes.overview: The campers meet two backwoods narwhals named Narlene and Nobby, who treat them to a sweet surprise.

episodes.name: Tag, You're It
episodes.overview: On a rainy day, SpongeBob and his friends entertain themselves indoors with a turbulent game of tag.

episodes.name: Quest for Tire
episodes.overview: The weekly food delivery truck goes missing, so the campers must hunt it down like their primal ancestors.

episodes.name: A Cabin of Curiosities
episodes.overview: A mysterious cabin of odd campers have frightful fun with SpongeBob and Patrick after dark.

episodes.name: In Search of Camp Noodist
episodes.overview: SpongeBob, Sandy, and Patrick hike through the woods in search of a fabled nudist colony.

episodes.name: Kitchen Sponge
episodes.overview: SpongeBob helps Plankton at the Krusty Kanteen, leading to the development of a very familiar sandwich.

episodes.name: The Treasure of Kamp Koral
episodes.overview: SpongeBob and Patrick find buried treasure at camp, but Mr. Krabs becomes desperate to get his claws on it.

episodes.name: Camper Gary
episodes.overview: SpongeBob disguises Gary as a new camper to keep him safe from Mrs. Puff.

episodes.name: Midnight Snack Attack
episodes.overview: After SpongeBob and Patrick eat a secret snack experiment, Plankton must reverse the monstrous side effects.

episodes.name: Hot Pearl-tato
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs needs to find a babysitter for little Pearl, but she proves too much for the campers to handle.

episodes.name: What About Meep?
episodes.overview: When an unsatisfied anchovy strays from his brothers, SpongeBob and Patrick must help him find his true identity.

episodes.name: Hard Time Out
episodes.overview: SpongeBob is sent to time out on behalf of his buddy, so Patrick does what he can to rectify the situation.

episodes.name: Pat's A Li'l Sinker
episodes.overview: Mrs. Puff gives swimming lessons to Patrick after realizing he never got his swim badge.

episodes.name: Camp SpongeBob
episodes.overview: SpongeBob finds himself all alone in the camp, but that doesn't stop him from having a blast.

episodes.name: Squisery
episodes.overview: Patrick and Squidward must survive together in the woods after Squidward twists all of his ankles.

episodes.name: Game Night
episodes.overview: The adults sneak away to play a board game, but they have to hide from one camper in particular.

episodes.name: My Fair Nobby
episodes.overview: When Nobby becomes too civilized for Narlene, SpongeBob and Patrick help him remember his backwoods ways.

episodes.name: Gimme a News Break
episodes.overview: Perch and his pal Harvey report the news of Kamp Koral, but they stumble upon evidence of a ridiculous conspiracy!

episodes.name: Wise Kraken
episodes.overview: It's stand-up comedy night at Kamp Koral, and the campers are ready to laugh until they scream.

episodes.name: Squatch Swap
episodes.overview: Patrick gets confused with a young Seasquatch while out in the woods.

episodes.name: The Ho! Ho! Horror!
episodes.overview: Santa Claus visits the children of Kamp Koral, who aren't quite sure what to make of the jolly giant.

episodes.name: Outhouse Outrage
episodes.overview: The outhouse explodes in front of Mr.Krabs, but he gets three different sides of the story from his campers.

episodes.name: Are You Afraid of the Dork?
episodes.overview: The counselors tell scary stories around the campfire, but things get truly spooky when a real ghost appears!

episodes.name: Help Not Wanted
episodes.overview: Patrick's dad unexpectedly visits Kamp Koral.

episodes.name: Camp Spirit
episodes.overview: SpongeBob, Patrick, and Sandy befriend a visiting ghost camper.

episodes.name: Hill-Fu
episodes.overview: It's the annual foam-fisted all-camp karate battle, and SpongeBob trains to beat the butt-kicking Sandy.

episodes.name: Sun’s Out, Fun’s Out
episodes.overview: It's the hottest day of summer, but there's only one AC in the whole camp.

episodes.name: First and Last Aid
episodes.overview: Camp Master Krabs finally hires a camp nurse, but she needs to dedicate all her time and effort to keeping SpongeBob safe.

episodes.name: Night of the Living Stench
episodes.overview: When all the campers try to win the 'Stinkiest Camp in the Forest' award, Squidward has to fend for his life to stay clean.

episodes.name: Camp Crossbones
episodes.overview: After SpongeBob, Patrick, and Sandy are banned from playing pirate outside, they decide to turn their cabin into a pirate ship.

episodes.name: The Jelly Life
episodes.overview: SpongeBob pretends to be a jellyfish for research purposes.

episodes.name: Lake Crashers
episodes.overview: The campers have a demolition derby under Lake Yuckymuck.

episodes.name: Boo Light Special
episodes.overview: Desperate for help, Camp Master Krabs hires the Flying Dutchman to run the camp store.

episodes.name: Painting with Squidward
episodes.overview: Counselor Squidward is determined for his cabin to win the annual camp art competition.

episodes.name: Kamp Kow
episodes.overview: The Kamp Koral campers befriend a cute cow with a big appetite.

episodes.name: Helter Shelter
episodes.overview: SpongeBob, Sandy, and Patrick are split up into separate cabins.

episodes.name: Reveille Revolution
episodes.overview: Squidward has to earn back his morning 'Reveille' duties.

episodes.name: The Switch Glitch
episodes.overview: An accident causes Patrick and Karen to switch bodies.

episodes.name: Prickly Pests
episodes.overview: A mischievous camp prank goes terribly wrong.

episodes.name: Are You Smarter Than a Smart Cabin?
episodes.overview: In an effort to avoid doing chores, Sandy invents a 'Smart Cabin.'

episodes.name: Deep Sea Despot
episodes.overview: Squidward takes over as Camp Master.

episodes.name: Regi-Hilled
episodes.overview: Narlene and Nobby teach Regigille all about backwoods living.

episodes.name: The Perfect Camper
episodes.overview: The Trawler cabin creates the perfect camper to compete in the Camp Summer Games.

episodes.name: Eye of the Hotdog
episodes.overview: Craig Mammalton learns what it's like to not be the best at something.

episodes.name: Patrick Takes the Cake
episodes.overview: Patrick and a cake hide out in the wilderness

episodes.name: Taste of Defeat
episodes.overview: Plankton discovers competition in Narlene's backwoods restaurant.

episodes.name: Scaredy Squirrel
episodes.overview: Sandy spends a night at the Trawler cabin.

episodes.name: Hats Off to Space
episodes.overview: The Dinghies travel to outer space.

episodes.name: In a Nut’s Shell
episodes.overview: After discovering his empty shell, Narlene and Nobby disguise themselves as Camp Master Krabs.

episodes.name: Mad Science Squirrel
episodes.overview: Plankton recruits Sandy to help in his lab.

episodes.name: To Pop a Bubble
episodes.overview: SpongeBob is determined to find out who popped his new bubble friend.

episodes.name: High and Dry
episodes.overview: The Dinghy cabin camps overnight out of the water.

episodes.name: The Beardsman
episodes.overview: Wilderness expert Paul Grunion visits the camp.

episodes.name: Five Times the Fun
episodes.overview: When Patrick’s detached limbs regrow into five Patrick clones, it’s up to the gang to stop them before they take over the camp.

episodes.name: Low Falutin
episodes.overview: Rea and Roh get a taste of the cheap life after they lose all their money.

episodes.name: Nut Madness
episodes.overview: Things get nutty at camp when Sandy goes feral over the sight of peanuts.

episodes.name: Mermaid Men and Barnacle Boys
episodes.overview: The Dinghy and Pontoon cabins go head-to-head in a series of superhero challenges.

episodes.name: A Tale of Two Roxies
episodes.overview: It’s a classic case of sibling rivalry after the conjoined Roxie sisters split up.

episodes.name: Nite Owls
episodes.overview: When the Dinghies attempt to stay up all night, they discover a side of camp they’ve never seen before.

episodes.name: Calling Some Monsters
episodes.overview: Realizing the monsters are actually quite boring, SpongeBob and Patrick set out to help them channel their wild side.

episodes.name: Dig This
episodes.overview: A mysterious bone discovery at Kamp Koral leads Sandy to start an archeological dig.

episodes.name: Un-Breaking and De-Entering
episodes.overview: SpongeBob discovers that Gary's been secretly taking items from everyone in camp.

episodes.name: Swimmin' Holed
episodes.overview: After SpongeBob and Patrick discover Narlene and Nobby's secret swimming hole, it doesn't stay a secret for long.

episodes.name: Krabsy the Klown
episodes.overview: When Mr. Krabs reveals that he used to be a clown, SpongeBob convinces him to wear the big shoes once again.

episodes.name: Lords of the LARP
episodes.overview: Mo joins the Pontoon cabin’s LARP (live action role-playing) group.

episodes.name: Mascot Mayhem
episodes.overview: SpongeBob and Patrick compete to become Kamp Koral's mascot.

episodes.name: Putt Up or Shut Up
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs and Squidward compete head-to-head to see who is the better golfer.

episodes.name: Who's Complaining?
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs puts Squidward in charge of Kamp Koral’s complaint department.

episodes.name: Patrick's Star
episodes.overview: SpongeBob and Sandy gift Patrick a star for his birthday.

episodes.name: A Finful of Sand Dollars
episodes.overview: Sheriff Sandy pulls out all the stops when a ne’er-do-well interloper turns Kamp Koral’s Western Day upside down.

episodes.name: Cretins of the Night
episodes.overview: SpongeBob and Patrick discover the ups and downs of vampire life with Kidferatu’s help.

episodes.name: The Suit Suits You
episodes.overview: Sandy learns the dangers of untested technology while an old companion goes on a journey of self-discovery.

episodes.name: Parasite Pals
episodes.overview: SpongeBob’s relationship with the rest of camp is pushed to the brink by his newest friend, a parasite living in his body.

episodes.name: End of Summer Daze
episodes.overview: Summer is over, and SpongeBob and Patrick stay behind for one final attempt to catch a jellyfish – but they’re not the only ones hiding out at camp.
